This is a list of summer schools of linguistics.
Expand list|date=November 2008 


* flagcountry|Germany: European Summer School in Logic, Language and Information (ESSLLI) - Hamburg (2008)<ref>cite web |url=http://www.illc.uva.nl/ESSLLI2008/ |title=ESSLLI 2008 |publisher=The Institute for Logic, Language and Computation</ref>
* flagcountry|Germany: Summer School on Corpus Phonology - Augsburg (2008)<ref>cite web |url=http://www.philhist.uni-augsburg.de/lehrstuehle/anglistik/applied/summerschool/ |title=Summer School on Corpus Phonology |publisher=Universität Augsburg</ref>
* flagcountry|Greece: The Crete Summer School of Linguistics (CreteLing) - Rethimnon (2017)<ref>cite web |url=http://www.phl.uoc.gr/confs/cssl17/ |title=The Crete Summer School of Linguistics |publisher=Department of Philology, University of Crete</ref>
* flagcountry|Hungary: European Summer School in Generative Grammar (EGG) - Debrecen (2014)<ref>cite web |url=http://www.eggschool.org/ |title=The Egg |publisher=Center for Advanced Study in Theoretical Linguistics, Universitetet i Tromsø</ref>
* flagcountry|Poland: Summer Institute "Languages and Cultures in Contact / in Contrast" - Zakopane (2008)<ref>cite web |url=http://silcc.pl |title=Summer Institute "Languages and Cultures in Contact / in Contrast"</ref>
* flagcountry|Portugal: NOVA - Lisbon Summer School and Graduate Conference in Linguistics - Lisbon<ref>cite web |url=http://www.clunl.edu.pt/pt/congressos.asp |title=NOVA - Lisbon Summer School and Graduate Conference in Linguistics</ref>
* flagcountry|Portugal: U. Minho - APL Summer School of Linguistics 2015: Experimental Methods in Syntax - Braga<ref>cite web |url=http://cehum.ilch.uminho.pt/summerschool2015#home |title=UMinho-APL Summer School of Linguistics</ref>
* flagcountry|UK: International Summer School in Forensic Linguistic Analysis - Birmingham (2000-2010)<ref>cite web |url=http://www.forensiclinguistics.eu |title=International Summer School in Forensic Linguistic Analysis</ref>
* flagcountry|US: Summer Institute of Linguistics - University of North Dakota (every summer)<ref>cite web |url=https://silund.org |title=Summer Institute of Linguistics, University of North Dakota (SIL-UND)</ref>
* flagcountry|US: Linguistics Society of America Summer Institutes, held in odd-numbered years, including:<ref>cite web |url=http://www.linguisticsociety.org/meetings-institutes |title=LSA Meetings & Institutes |publisher=Linguistic Society of America</ref>
** Empirical Foundations for Theories of Language - Stanford (2007)<ref>cite web |url=http://linginst07.stanford.edu/ |title=Linguistics Society of America Summer Institute |publisher=Stanford University |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071009221859/http://linginst07.stanford.edu/ |archivedate=2007-10-09 |df= </ref>
** Linguistic Structure and Language Ecologies - UC Berkeley (2009)<ref>cite web |url=http://lsa2009.berkeley.edu/ |title=LSA 2009 |publisher=University of California, Berkeley</ref>
** Language in the World - University of Colorado at Boulder (2011)<ref>cite web |url=http://verbs.colorado.edu/LSA2011/ |title=LSA 2011 |publisher=University of Colorado, Boulder</ref>
** Universality and Variability - University of Michigan (2013)<ref>cite web |url=http://lsa2013.lsa.umich.edu/ |title=LSA 2013 |publisher=University of Michigan</ref>
** Linguistic Theory in a World of Big Data - University of Chicago (2015)<ref>Cite web|url = https://lsa2015.uchicago.edu/|title = LSA 2015|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = University of Chicago|last = |first = </ref>
** Language Across Space and Time - University of Kentucky (2017)<ref>Cite web|url=http://lsa2017.uky.edu/|title=LSA 2017 ! 2017 Linguistic Institute|website=lsa2017.uky.edu|access-date=2016-06-30</ref>
* InField (Institute on Field Linguistics and Language Documentation) and its successor CoLang (Institute on Collaborative Language Research), held in even-numbered years, including:
** flagcountry|US: InField - University of California, Santa Barbara (2008)<ref>cite web |url=http://www.linguistics.ucsb.edu/faculty/infield/ |title=InField 2008 |publisher=University of California, Santa Barbara</ref>
