** flagcountry|US: CoLang - University of Florida (2018)
* flagcountry|Netherlands: LOT Winter School - Groningen (city)|Groningen (2009)<ref>cite web |url=http://wwwlot.let.uu.nl/ |title=Netherlands Graduate School of Linguistics |publisher=Universiteit Utrecht</ref>
